qDef.qDef:
'YTD '&
MonthName(Max({1<[Month ID]={$(v_Max_Month_ID)}>}[Month Year]))

(
	$(v_Sales_Contribution_Amount_YTD)
    -
    Pick(
		$(v_Switch_Option_LY_BUD)
	    ,$(v_Sales_Contribution_Amount_LY_YTD)
		,$(v_Budget_Contribution_Amount_YTD)
	    )
)/1000

Pick(
	$(v_Switch_Option_LY_BUD)
    ,
    if(
		Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY)"},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])=0
	   
	    ,//True
		$(v_Sales_Contribution_Amount_YTD)

    	,//False
	    (
	    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
	        -
	    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY)"},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
		)
	    *
		$(v_Sales_Contribution_Amount_LY_YTD)
		/
		Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY)"},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
	)
	,
    if
	(
		Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])=0
	   
	    ,//True
		$(v_Budget_Contribution_Amount_YTD)

    	,//False
	    (
	    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
	        -
	    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])

	)/1000

byMeasureDef.label: This Period
byMeasureDef.key:
Pick
(
	$(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD)
    ,
    Pick
    (
        $(v_Selected_Measure_One)
        ,//MT
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
        ,//Amount
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
        /1000
        ,//COP
        (
            (
              Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
              -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
            )
        )/1000
    )
    ,
    Pick
    (
        $(v_Selected_Measure_One)
        ,//MT
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
        ,//Amount
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
        /1000
        ,//COP
        $(v_Sales_Contribution_Amount_YTD)
        /1000
    )
)

qDef.qDef:
Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
/
Pick(
	$(v_Switch_Option_LY_BUD)
    ,sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
	,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'},$(v_B2C_Sales_Filter),$(v_Neutralize_Filter), [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
    )

qStringExpression.qExpr:
='QTY vs.'&
Pick(
	$(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD)
    ,'None'
  	,'None'
    ,'Last Year :'
	&
	Num(
		Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
		/
		Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
	    *100
    	,Text('#,##0')
	    ,","
    	,"."
	    )
	,'Budget :'
	&
	Num(
		Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
		/
		Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
	    *100
    	,Text('#,##0')
	    ,","
    	,"."
	    )
	)
&' %'
